question: Get all records from the Stock table
predicted_sql: SELECT DISTINCT s.id FROM Stock s JOIN Orders o ON s.id = o.id WHERE o.quantity > 0

question: List the IDs of products in stock with their current quantity
predicted_sql: SELECT DISTINCT id FROM Stock WHERE id IN (SELECT id FROM Orders)

question: Get the average unit price of all products in stock
expected_sql: SELECT AVG(unit_price) AS avg_unit_price FROM Stock;

question: Find products with more than 10,000 units in stock
expected_sql: SELECT id, current_stock_quantity FROM Stock WHERE current_stock_quantity > 10000;

question: Get the total quantity of products in stock
expected_sql: SELECT SUM(current_stock_quantity) AS total_stock FROM Stock;

question: Get the product with the highest maximum lead time
